txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Coarse fur from the beasts to the west of Esteldín. Deliver the items to Ferrif within Esteldín.
'We will put these to good use. Thank you.'
'We are short on supplies for those that need the most help. We need every bit of supplies that we can gather. Furs from the beasts to the west will be a good starting point.'
Rangers of Esteldín Task: Coarse Fur
Ferrif, a Ranger, has asked for a collection of coarse fur to be delivered to him at the Ranger's home at Esteldín.
Deliver the coarse fur to Ferrif in Esteldín
You have accepted a task to collect coarse fur from the beasts in the area surrounding Esteldín to the west. Once collected, you are to deliver the items to Ferrif within Esteldín.
Wanted: Coarse fur from the beasts to the west of Esteldín.
